body_raw:
So this is a result used in Peter Topping's, Lectures on Ricci Flow . What is a quick of showing $$	ext{tr}
abla_{X,\cdot}^2h(\cdot,W)=-(
abla\delta h)(X,W)$$ where $\delta A=-	ext{tr}_{12}
abla A$, is the divergence operator and $h=\partial_tg$.

